-- Investors in Talks to Build Bahrain Steel Plant, Al-Wasat Says
-- B y   D o n n a   A b u - N a s r
-- 2012-01-29T07:40:53Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-29/investors-in-talks-to-build-bahrain-steel-plant-al-wasat-says.html
Investors are in talks to build a
steel plant in Bahrain with as much as a 500,000 ton capacity,
 Al-Wasat newspaper reported  today, citing unidentified industry
officials.  A Japanese company may be among the investors, the paper
said, without giving further details.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Donna Abu Nasr in Manama at 
 dabunasr@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
